data.text:
Office for rent in Bandar Tun Hussein Onn Cheras. This unit is on the 2nd floor bare unit available immediately for occupancy. Located 2 lot away from Mary Brown and opposite of Citibank Bandar Tun Hussien Onn. Large floor area of 24x80ft.

Specification of the property are as follow:

Built-up : Approx. 1900sf

Type: Intermediate

2 toilets

Condition: Unfurnished

Near Mary Brown, Citibank, Zakat Selangor & AEON Big Bandar Tun Hussein Onn.

Minimum contract 2yrs

Rental rate: RM1,700/month
